				<title>Re: Command line Quizzes</title>
				<description><![CDATA[ Bài 2:
Thay nhân chia cộng trừ bằng việc cắt thẳng thằng đó:
<span class="quotetxt"><b>Code:</b></span><br/>
		<div class="coded"">
		<pre>for &#40;&#40;i=1; i&lt;11; i++&#41;&#41;; do
   Hien=""
   for &#40;&#40;j=1; j&lt;11; j++&#41;&#41;; do
      Hien="${Hien} ${RANDOM:1:1}"
   done
   echo $Hien
done</pre>
		</div>
]]></description>
